p><p>The remote also allows you to set your own custom power level, giving you even more flexibility to match your riding style.&nbsp;<\/p><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-8013 lazyload\" style=\"aspect-ratio:16\/9;object-fit:cover\"\/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2240\" height=\"1260\" src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-8013 lazyload\" style=\"aspect-ratio:16\/9;object-fit:cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2.jpg 2240w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2-60x34.jpg 60w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/3-2-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2240px) 100vw, 2240px\" \/><\/noscript><\/figure><\/div><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Designed for safety and personalisation<\/h2><p>The Series 2 Remote also offers a configurable throttle safety lock timer, which prevents accidental throttle engagement, increasing the level of safety the Stoke offers, especially for new riders.<\/p><p>For a bit of fun, we&#8217;ve also included three different theme colours so you can add your own vibe to the remote.<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Compatible with the Stoke Foil Boost<\/h2><p>There will be no switching up your equipment if you decide to upgrade to our new remote. This remote will sync up perfectly with whichever Stoke you are currently riding, giving you the smoothest possible experience every time.<\/p><p>For those still learning, this remote will make foiling more approachable and less intimidating. You can gradually build up your confidence without being overwhelmed by too much power too quickly. For advanced riders, this remote will give you the performance edge you\u2019re after. You\u2019ll have more control and responsiveness at your fingertips, allowing you to push your foiling skills further.<\/p><p>Stoke continues to bring the future of foiling your way, and this latest innovation fits right in the palm of your hand.<\/p><p>Order your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/product\/series-2-remote-receiver\/\">Series 2 Remote and Receiver<\/a> today.<\/p><p><\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We&#8217;re confident that the new Series 2 Remote will become your new best friend on the water. It&#8217;s stacked with features to improve your ride. Learn more.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":36,"featured_media":8011,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8004","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-gofoiling"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8004","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/36"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/co